<L>__{exterior marty and brady kincaid magic hour}
<A>__{they're flying kites on the common. some distance in the b.g. is the bandstand. marty is of course flying his kite as he sits in the silver bullet. the boys are having a blast. the camera slowly moves away from the boys, centers on owen's pub across the street, and zooms in. in the window is a poster. it reads: $10,000 reward for information leading to the capture of the man (or animal) who killed stella randolph and milton sturmfuller. and, at the bottom: tarker's mills citizens' committee. along comes andy fairton. he goes into the pub.}
